Udi bụ Obodo Gọọmentị nke Enugwu Steeti, Naịjirịa
Isi ụlọ ọrụ ya dị n'obodo Udi n'okporo ụzọ awara awara A232
Onye isi oche nke gọọmentị ime obodo ugbu a bụ Hon Ifeanyi Agu.
O nwere mpaghara nke 897 km2 na ọnụ ọgụgụ mmadụ nke 370,002 na ọnụego afọ 2015.
Koodu ozi nke mpaghara ahụ bụ 401.
Ọ bụ isiokwu nke ihe nkiri ihe nkiri nke afọ 1949 Daybreak in Udi
Ezinụlọ Umuneke, nke nwere obodo ndị a: Udi / Agbudu, Abia, Obinagu, Umuabi Ezike, Omashi-Amaji Umuabi, Umuaga, Oji Amokwe, Enugwu Amokwe, Etiti Amokwe, Uwani Amokwe na Nachi
Udi bụ onye okenye n'ezinụlọ na Umuneke
Ezedike: Akpakwume, Ibute Nze, Ezi Nze, Oghu
Ojebogene: Awhum, Ebe, Abor, Umuavulu, Abor، Ukana, Awhum، Okpatu-Ikeghe, Okpatu, Ibite, Umulumbge, Umuoka.
Ngwo : Ngwo Asaa, Imeama Ngwo Asa, Ameke Ngwo, Uboji Ngwo, Amankwo Ngwo.
